Cloud Infrastructure:

1. Full virtualisation
  + Unique applications
  + Different operating systems
  + One way to access services on the cloud

2. Ideal for
  + Sharing computer system among multiple users
  + isolating users from each other.
  + emulating hardwares on another machines

3. Paravirtualisation
  + multiple operating systems run on other devices simultaneously
  + not all elements need be emulated.
  + allows for better scaling

4. Ideal for the purpose of 
  + disaster recovery
  + migration
